        <ul style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 2;">
            <li>Ravens can live 20+ years in the wild and over 40 years in captivity</li>
            <li>They can mimic human speech and various sounds</li>
            <li>Ravens can recognize individual human faces</li>
            <li>They demonstrate play behavior rare in birds</li>
            <li>Ravens have been observed using tools and teaching their young</li>
            <li>A group of ravens is called an "unkindness" or "conspiracy"</li>
            <li>Ravens communicate with complex vocalizations and body language</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
